FBIS4-28949 "dreas115_c_94028" FBIS-EAS-94-115 Daily Report 12 Jun 1994 North Korea ROK Subway Trade Union Threatens To Strike ROK Subway Trade Union Threatens To Strike SK1206101894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0805 GMT 12 Jun 94 SK1206101894 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 12 (KCNA) -- The council of the South Korean Subway Trade Union on Thursday called a press conference and urged the puppet authorities to lift the wage ceiling, according to a radio report. The trade union warned that it would launch into a general strike that would cause a total suspension of the operation of railways and subways throughout South Korea in case the present "regime" physically put down its demand as the past military regimes had done.
